    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every thousand years it is said that a great evil emerges with one purpose: to bring Chaos to this realm. Unopposed, it would smother the light from our world and  bathe it in darkness. As the legend goes... there is but one who could stand against the rising shadow and vanquish its evil, people call this hero the Doomwalker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight fantastical creatures, grow your power, unlock powerful upgrades and abilities, become the Doomwalker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in a distant land, Doomwalker is an immersive Action RPG that confronts you with a devious plot which seeks to bring destruction to your home, friends, and village. Along the way, however, you discover that not everything is as it seems. You will need more than your wits if you wish to survive.</p>",
